        <br>
        <p>Decentralized & Unregulated: RoulFi operates under a fully decentralized model. We have no plans to adopt any centralized regulation, meaning no account bans, no multi-account restrictions, and no identity verification requirements.</p>
        <br>
        <p>Privacy First: We do not enforce AML (Anti-Money Laundering) or KYC (Know Your Customer) checks, ensuring complete anonymity for all players.</p>
        <br>
        <p>Core Game – Roulette: Our primary game is Roulette, offering a seamless, trustless, and autonomous gaming experience.</p>
        <br>
        <p>Chat Content Moderation Only: The only regulation in place is chat moderation to maintain a fair and respectful community. No other restrictions apply.</p>
        <br>
