      <section class="discover__section" id="privacy">
        <h2 class="discover__title">Privacy</h2>
        <p>At RoulFi, privacy isn’t just a feature it’s a principle. We are committed to ensuring complete anonymity for our users.</p>
        <br>
        <p>- We do not collect, store, or analyze any personal data.</p>
        <br>
        <p>- We do not track IP addresses, use cookies for analytics, or attempt to profile users in any way.</p>
        <br>
        <p>
          The only information stored in our databases includes:
              <br>- Game history
              <br>- Betting history
              <br>- Deposit & withdrawal history
              <br>- Wallet address linked to the account (since registration is done via wallet authentication)
        </p>
        <br>
        <p>Your data is your business, not ours.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="discover__section" id="coin-mixing">
        <h2 class="discover__title">Coin Mixing</h2>
        <p>RoulFi is not a crypto-mixing service, but we prioritize player security and anonymity.</p>
        <br>
        <p>- Withdrawals are processed from shared liquidity pools, ensuring that deposit and withdrawal histories are not directly linked.</p>
        <br>
        <p>- This mechanism enhances privacy by making it harder to trace transactions, similar to how crypto mixers function.</p>
        <br>
        <p>- However, unlike traditional mixing services, our system is fully transparent and operates autonomously within the decentralized ecosystem.</p>
        <br>
        <p>Your funds remain secure, untraceable, and decentralized the way DeFi was meant to be.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="discover__section" id="project-mirrors-and-tor-access">
        <h2 class="discover__title">Project Mirrors & Tor Access</h2>
        <p>At RoulFi, we embrace true decentralization, but we recognize that our model may face opposition from regulatory forces. To ensure uninterrupted access, we provide an official Tor (Onion) mirror for enhanced privacy and censorship resistance.</p>
        <br>
        <p>- Our Tor mirror allows users to access RoulFi securely, even in regions with restrictions.</p>
        <br>
        <p>- New mirrors may be introduced as needed to bypass censorship and maintain availability.</p>
        <br>
        <p>- We are committed to staying online, regardless of external pressures.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="discover__section" id="deposits-and-withdrawals">
        <h2 class="discover__title">Deposits&ensp;<span class="accent">&</span>&ensp;Withdrawals</h2>
        <p>At RoulFi, we ensure secure, fast, and private transactions through our automated system.</p>
        <br>
        <p>- When making a deposit, a unique wallet address is generated for your account within the same network. This deposit address is permanently linked to your account for future transactions.</p>
        <br>
        <p>- Deposits are credited once the system detects full confirmation on the blockchain.</p>
        <br>
        <p>- Withdrawals are automated and processed from a shared liquidity pool, enhancing privacy by unlinking deposit and withdrawal histories similar to a crypto mixer.</p>
        <br>
        <p>- To withdraw funds, a player must first wager at least 1x the deposit amount to prevent abuse and maintain liquidity.</p>
      </section>
